Package ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services

Interface PeriodService

All Known Implementing Classes:
PeriodServiceImpl
@Service public interface PeriodService
Service interface for handling operations related to periods.

This interface defines the contract for managing Period instances, including retrieving the current period.
